	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">那个卖芯片的高通，怎么找《鸟人》编剧、王力宏拍起了电影？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-13 15:21:06 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">1</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">2</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/26797.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
